item.title: [+499] California bond allows private companies control of water
item.description: Private companies could make a profit by selling water back to the public under a little-noticed provision in California's $11.1 billion water bond. In a state where water is an especially precious resource, critics worry that giving control of this resource to private companies is a recipe for disaster.
